{"title":"我用回了Hexo","date":"2021-01-07T05:18:09.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"Jan 7, 2021","L":"01/07/2021","MM-DD":"01-07"},"link":"2021/01/07/reset","updated":"2021-01-22T15:09:16.857Z","content":"<link rel=\"stylesheet\" class=\"aplayer-secondary-style-marker\" href=\"/assets/css/APlayer.min.css\"><script src=\"/assets/js/APlayer.min.js\" class=\"aplayer-secondary-script-marker\"></script><script class=\"meting-secondary-script-marker\" src=\"/assets/js/Meting.min.js\"></script><p>从最开始整博客，我使用的是HEXO。它除了写文章比较麻烦之外，没有啥太大的缺点。但是中途我为了更方便的编辑和发布文章，改用了Typecho。直到…</p>\n<p>我的博客炸了。</p>\n<p>早上一打开博客，发现Typecho畸形错位，想想算了，换回HEXO吧。就这样，我改回来了。</p>\n<p>如果没有改回HEXO，我一辈子都不会发现它是那么的简单，全程没有看任何的笔记，就那么行云流水的完成了。</p>\n","prev":{"title":"FileRun+NextCloud实现图床和备份","link":"2021/01/31/imagebackup"},"next":{"title":"Jellyfin主题管理插件","link":"2021/01/01/jellyfin-theme"},"plink":"https://0x01x0.ml/2021/01/07/reset/"}